msgid "Build a strong foundation for your future career"
msgstr "Kelajak karyerangiz uchun mustahkam poydevor yarating"

msgid "Choose from programs in Business & Economics, IT, Education, Foreign Languages, and Jurisprudence. Our bachelor's degrees combine international standards with practical skills, preparing you for the global job market."
msgstr "Biznes va Iqtisodiyot, IT, Pedagogika, Xorijiy tillar va Huquqshunoslik dasturlaridan tanlang. Bakalavr dasturlarimiz xalqaro standartlarni amaliy ko'nikmalar bilan birlashtiradi."

msgid "Deepen your expertise and advance your career"
msgstr "Bilimingizni chuqurlashtiring va karyerangizni rivojlantiring"

msgid "Our master's programs in Public Finance, International Finance, and Economics offer advanced research opportunities and expert faculty. Take the next step in your academic and professional journey."
msgstr "Davlat moliyasi, Xalqaro moliya va Iqtisodiyot bo'yicha magistratura dasturlarimiz ilg'or tadqiqot imkoniyatlari va tajribali professor-o'qituvchilarni taklif etadi."

msgid "Lead research and shape the future of your field"
msgstr "Tadqiqotlarga rahbarlik qiling va soha kelajagini shakllantiring"

msgid "Our doctoral programs in Finance, Economics, and Management prepare you for careers in academia and research leadership. Work alongside internationally recognized scholars on cutting-edge projects."
msgstr "Moliya, Iqtisodiyot va Menejment bo'yicha doktorantura dasturlarimiz akademik va ilmiy rahbarlik karyerasiga tayyorlaydi."

msgid "program — study here,"
msgstr "dasturi — bu yerda o'qing,"

msgid "graduate there."
msgstr "u yerda bitiring."

msgid "Our unique dual degree program offers you the best of both worlds. Spend your first two years at TIU in Tashkent, then complete your studies at one of our prestigious partner universities abroad. Graduate with two internationally recognized degrees that open doors to global career opportunities."
msgstr "Noyob qo'shma diplom dasturimiz ikki dunyoning eng yaxshisini taklif etadi. Birinchi ikki yilni TIU da o'tkazib, o'qishingizni xorijdagi sherik universitetlardan birida yakunlang."

msgid "Five dynamic faculties,"
msgstr "Beshta dinamik fakultet,"

msgid "one bold vision."
msgstr "bitta jasur qarash."

msgid "Choose from cutting-edge departments: Business for future entrepreneurs, Education for tomorrow's teachers, IT for tech innovators, Foreign Languages for global communicators, and Jurisprudence for legal minds. Each offers programs taught by international faculty."
msgstr "Ilg'or fakultetlardan tanlang: kelajak tadbirkorlar uchun Biznes, ertangi o'qituvchilar uchun Pedagogika, texnologik innovatorlar uchun IT, global muloqotchilar uchun Xorijiy tillar va huquqchilar uchun Huquqshunoslik."

msgid "More than lectures —"
msgstr "Ma'ruzalardan ko'proq —"

msgid "this is where you grow."
msgstr "bu siz o'sadigan joy."

msgid "Join 50+ student clubs, participate in sports tournaments, cultural festivals, and hackathons. Our students organize TEDx events, volunteer projects, and international exchange programs. TIU is not just a university — it's a community where you build lifelong friendships."
msgstr "50+ talabalar klublariga qo'shiling, sport musobaqalari, madaniy festivallar va hakatonlarda ishtirok eting. TIU nafaqat universitet — bu umrbod do'stlik qurish jamoasi."

msgid "Our campus is in the center of Tashkent — minutes from Amir Temur Square and major metro stations. Modern lecture halls, coworking spaces, and a well-equipped library create the perfect environment for learning."
msgstr "Kampusimiz Toshkent markazida — Amir Temur maydonidan bir necha daqiqa masofada. Zamonaviy auditoriyalar, kovorking va jihozlangan kutubxona o'qish uchun mukammal muhit yaratadi."

