msgid "Tashkent International University — a modern private university providing world-class education in the heart of Uzbekistan."
msgstr "Tashkent International University — O'zbekiston qalbida jahon darajasidagi ta'lim beruvchi zamonaviy xususiy universitet."

msgid "Join Tashkent International University and step into a world of academic excellence, personal growth, and limitless opportunities."
msgstr "TIUga qo'shiling — akademik mukammallik, shaxsiy o'sish va cheksiz imkoniyatlar dunyosiga qadam qo'ying."

msgid "University"
msgstr "Universitet"

msgid "Modern Campus Life"
msgstr "Zamonaviy kampus muhiti"

msgid "Our modern campus, located on the Small Ring Road in the center of Tashkent, offers everything needed for academic success and personal development. Modern classrooms, healthcare facilities, student clubs, a contemporary dormitory, and a vibrant community are waiting for you. At TIU, you will find the perfect environment for learning, networking, and growth."
msgstr "Toshkentning markazidagi Kichik Halqa Yo'lda joylashgan zamonaviy kampusimiz akademik muvaffaqiyat va shaxsiy rivojlanish uchun zarur bo'lgan hamma narsani taqdim etadi. Zamonaviy sinflar, sog'liqni saqlash inshootlari, talabalar klublari, zamonaviy talabalar yotoqxonasi va jonli hamjamiyat sizni kutmoqda. TIUda siz o'rganish, aloqalarni o'rnatish va taraqqiyot uchun mukammal muhit topasiz."

msgid "International Programs"
msgstr "Xalqaro dasturlar"

msgid "2+2 Program"
msgstr "2+2 programa dasturi"

msgid "Students studying under the 2+2 program at TIU and prestigious international partner universities earn two diplomas. The program provides a wide range of skills, global experience, and competitive advantage in a short period."
msgstr "TIU va nufuzli xorijiy hamkor universitetlarda 2+2 dasturida o'qib, talabalar ikki diplomga ega bo'lishadi. Dastur qisqa vaqt ichida keng ko'nikmalar, global tajriba va raqobatbardosh ustunlik beradi."

msgid "TIU's academic exchange program is organized in partnership with international universities. It allows students to study abroad, gain international experience, and expand their academic and cultural skills."
msgstr "Tashkent International University (TIU) talabalari uchun xalqaro universitetlar bilan hamkorlik asosida tashkil etilgan akademik almashinuv dasturidir. Ushbu dastur talabalarga chet el universitetlarida o'qish, xalqaro tajriba olish va o'z bilim hamda madaniy ko'nikmalarini kengaytirish imkonini beradi."

msgid "TIU students have the opportunity to participate in internships at partner universities and organizations abroad. The program enables students to develop professional, language, and cultural skills while building a global professional network. The university's International Relations Office supports students in finding internship placements and managing all organizational matters."
msgstr "TIU talabalari amaliyot (internship) dasturini chetdagi hamkor universitetlar va tashkilotlarda o'tkazish imkoniga ega. Bu dastur orqali talabalar xorijiy ish muhitida kasbiy tajriba, til va madaniy ko'nikmalarni rivojlantirish hamda global professional tarmoq yaratish imkoniyatiga ega bo'ladilar. Universitet Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi talabalarni amaliyot joylarini topishda va barcha tashkilotchilik masalalarida qo'llab-quvvatlaydi."

msgid "WHERE KNOWLEDGE MEETS OPPORTUNITY"
msgstr "BILIM VA IMKONIYATLAR BIRLASHGAN MASKAN"

msgid "Tashkent International University (TIU) is a modern private university located in Tashkent, established in October 2023. TIU develops partnerships with prestigious international universities and organizations, offering students wide-ranging academic opportunities. Our main goal is to provide students with a solid foundation for success in their chosen careers and life. Start building your future today — join TIU."
msgstr "Tashkent International University (TIU) — Toshkent shahrida joylashgan zamonaviy xususiy universitet bo'lib, 2023-yil oktyabr oyida tashkil etilgan. TIU nufuzli xorijiy universitetlar va tashkilotlar bilan hamkorlikni rivojlantirib, talabalarga keng akademik imkoniyatlar yaratadi. Bizning asosiy maqsadimiz — talabalarimizni tanlagan kasbi va hayot yo'lida muvaffaqiyatga erishishlari uchun mustahkam poydevor bilan ta'minlash. Kelajagingizni bugundan boshlang — TIUga qo'shiling."

msgid "2+2 DUAL DEGREE"
msgstr "2+2 QO'SHMA DIPLOM"

msgid "STUDENT EXCHANGE"
msgstr "TALABA ALMASHUVI"

msgid "Student Exchange Program"
msgstr "Talaba almashuv dasturi"

msgid "INTERNSHIP"
msgstr "AMALIYOT"

msgid "Internship Program"
msgstr "Amaliyot dasturi"
